{
  "texts": [
    "RNA and DNA were extracted using TRIzol (Invitrogen, 15596026) following the manufacturer's instructions.",
    "Total RNA was then processed through an RNeasy kit (Qiagen, 74106) followed by oncolumn DNA digestion.",
    "RNA was converted to cDNA using Maxima H Minus Reverse Transcriptase (Thermo Fisher Scientific, EP0751) according to the manufacturer's instructions.",
    "Samples were then processed as detailed in the \"NGS sample preparation\" section.",
    "Neutralization assays were performed at 500 or 1000 vector genomes (vg)/cell in Perkin-Elmer white 96-well plates."
  ]
}